      "restriction_enzymes": "Restriction enzyme",
      "bacterial_proteins_that_cut_dna_at_spe": "ਬੈਕਟੀਰੀਆ protein ਜੋ ਖਾਸ 4-8 bp sequence ਉੱਤੇ DNA ਕੱਟਦੇ ਹਨ। recombinant DNA technology ਸੰਭਵ ਬਣਾਈ। Nobel 1978।",
      "dna_ligase": "DNA ligase",
