      "read_lengths_up_to_100kb_vs_illumina_s": "Read length 100 kb+ ਤੱਕ (Illumina ਦੇ ~300 bp ਦੇ ਮੁਕਾਬਲੇ)। structural variant, repeat, full-length transcript ਲਈ ਬਿਹਤਰ।",
